sensor_unavailable.description:
The {sensor_type} sensor '{sensor_name}' in group '{group_name}' is unavailable because {unavailable_count} tracked entities are unavailable.

Unavailable entities: {unavailable_entities}

Please check these entities to restore functionality.

upstream_unavailable.description:
The upstream sensor for group '{group_name}' is unavailable.

Unavailable entity: {upstream_entity}

This affects power monitoring and remainder calculations. Please check the upstream entity to restore functionality.

all_devices_unavailable.description:
All {device_count} devices in the Phantom group '{group_name}' are unavailable.

Unavailable devices: {device_list}

This affects all power monitoring, energy tracking, and cost calculations for this group. Please check your device entities to restore functionality.
